        &nbsp;<a href="post.asp?method=ReplyQuote&amp;REPLY_ID=73190&amp;TOPIC_ID=8464&amp;FORUM_ID=17&amp;CAT_ID=1&amp;Forum_Title=Rant+Forum&amp;Topic_Title=Wurmslayer+I+hate+this+weapon&amp;M="><img src="icon_reply_topic.gif" height="15" width="15" alt="Reply with Quote" border="0" align="absmiddle" hspace="6"></a>

        <hr noshade size="2" color="#545A7D">
        
         Alright I too have a warrior... he's a 57 halfling warrior when i was the lvl that all other warriors were using the wurmslayer ya wanna know what i used? a Kunzar Ku'juch (8/22 proc engulfling darkness) and a Green Jade Broadsword (11/25 +nice stats) now from personal experience at lvl 45 i was able to pull aggro offa the lvl 50 warriors in my group. Now any warrior above lvl 50 using a wurmy is a retard they should at least upgrade to a Lammy i mean on my server they go for 2k max me? what am i using? a Fleshgrinder (12/19 proc 160DD) and a Horn of Hsagra (13/20 awsome stats) with these two weapons i am able to pull aggro off of epic warriors as long as i get a proc. Now the thing with the "but if i do so much dmg why would i lose aggro" well heres why. Lets say your using a wurmmy 25/40 and i dunno a FS long sword 6/28 well the way duel weild works is every time your primary hand swings the game rolls to see if you get to attack with your offhand so with that 40 delay its only rolling to see if you hit with your off hand every 4 seconds. so lets say you swing at ubermob_01 and hit great you do 50 points of dmg you make your duel weild roll great another 12 points of dmg you make your double attack roll for both weapons great! damn you missed with that wurmmy swing and hit with the FS another 12.thats 74 points of dmg total! now you get to sit there for 4 seconds and do nothing.<BR>Now same situation cept i'm using a lammy 9/19 and a FS longsword 6/28<BR>well i swing and hit for 18 points of dmg i hit with my FS too! great 12 more dmg i make the double attack rolls too! but i miss with the lammy and hit with the FS for 12 thats 42 dmg so far! yay! now while your still sitting there with your 40 dly i'm swinging again wham i hit with my lammy and my FS 18 and 12 wham i make my double attack hit with the lammy for 18 but miss with the FS so now 4 seconds is over... i've done a total of 90 points of dmg... you did a total of 74 now yes i know the dmg isnt that accurate but you get the point. =D now if the lammy and the wurmmy also had a proc the lammy would have had 4 chances to proc in 4 seconds but the wurmmy woulda only had two... thats why faster weapons end up holding more aggro. thank ya for listening to me =)</P><P> <a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
